the eldest daughter of the Lu family.

57
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,960
The current eldest daughter

58
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,240
is Lu Chuning.

59
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:37,640
Father-in-law,

60
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,680
