be the wisest choice.

82
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,400
You...

83
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:38,920
Let's go.

84
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,080
You can't marry her.

85
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,920
