to become fodder for street gossip?

91
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,440
Uncle, it's rare for you
to sound reasonable.

92
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,920
It's actually quite unsettling.

93
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:01,680
Chuning!

94
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:04,200
Show some respect to your uncle!

95
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,960
What kind of uncle am I?

96
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,520
I share no blood with the Lu family.

97
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,120
To be honest,

98
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,160
Chuning and I

99
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,760
