102
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:20,640
I should've shot you back then.

103
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,440
Wait.

104
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,120
Say that again. What did you just say?

105
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,080
What did you say?

106
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:30,400
Brother...

107
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,360
If you're angry, then take it out on me.

108
00:05:33,794 --> 00:05:34,640
Back then,

109
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,720
when Chuning confessed
her feelings to me,

110
00:05:36,851 --> 00:05:38,520
I couldn't help myself.

111
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,560
But at the time,

112
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,520
