114
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,480
But don't worry.

115
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,640
For the rest of Chuning's life,

116
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,560
I'll take care of her.

117
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,440
I'll support her.

118
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:52,880
Chuning...

119
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:55,040
What's going on here?

120
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,000
