121
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,440
Do you believe him?

122
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:02,720
Master.

123
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,560
Back home, we have a method

124
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,400
to test whether a woman's still pure.

125
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,680
But I'm afraid

126
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,120
