127
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,680
Asking an innocent girl
to prove her innocence?

128
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,600
You have no right to demand that.

129
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:18,120
After what she's done,

130
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,600
