133
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,040
If you care about her,

134
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,480
you shouldn't stop us.

135
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:29,080
Alright.

136
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,000
Father,

137
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,720
I'll go with them.

138
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,440
Ms. Lin,

139
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,000
I'll need a drop of your blood.

140
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:36,800
Siyan,

141
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:37,920
