142
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,400
This way, Ms. Lin.

143
00:06:41,291 --> 00:06:41,828
Brother.

144
00:06:42,205 --> 00:06:43,091
Let me explain.

145
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,000
Please don't blame me.

146
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,080
You know me.

147
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,040
This is just how I am.

148
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,360
I really didn't know
she was your daughter.

149
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,360
So I just...

150
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:50,680
Shut up!

151
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,520
This is Ms. Lin's blood.

152
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,880
We drop it on a budding yellow flower.

153
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,840
If the flower stays fresh,
she's still pure.

154
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,160
If it wilts,

155
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,320
then she's lost her chastity.

156
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:27,960
Father...

157
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,080
Don't call me that!

158
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,040
I have no daughter as shameless as you.

159
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:34,960
Father-in-law,

160
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,160
I'm willing to marry Chuning.

161
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,840
Are you serious?

162
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,200
You don't mind her past?

163
00:07:43,794 --> 00:07:45,360
I, Shen Mochen, swear here and now,

164
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,200
that I will marry her with full honor,

165
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,360
with full bridal attire,

166
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,600
with drums and gongs,

167
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,480
and bring Chuning home.

168
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,760
Still not saying anything?

169
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,320
If you stay silent now,

170
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,160
your future might be decided.

171
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,120
Uncle...

172
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,040
You said

173
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,440
you've been intimate with me.

174
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,040
Then tell me,

175
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,560
is the birthmark on my waist

176
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,680
on the left

177
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:08,640
or the right?

178
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,120
Birthmark?

179
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:12,720
It's

180
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,120
