when she drew blood.

184
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,040
Didn't you?

185
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,280
Tell them.

186
00:08:22,502 --> 00:08:23,120
That's right.

187
00:08:23,382 --> 00:08:24,240
It's on the right.

188
00:08:24,982 --> 00:08:25,880
Wrong again.

189
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:28,320
I don't have a birthmark
on my waist at all.

190
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:29,920
Why did you lie?

191
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,800
Just now...

192
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,680
I...

193
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,520
I didn't notice while drawing the blood.

194
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,560
Chuning.

195
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,400
Even if your uncle
didn't take your chastity,

196
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,040
you're still not pure.

197
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,320
That is clear.

198
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,960
A woman must respect herself.

199
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,520
From now on,
live a good life with Mochen.

200
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,400
Don't ever degrade yourself again.

201
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,120
Well said, Mother.

202
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:53,280
A girl must respect and love herself.

203
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:55,520
But that blood just now was mine.

204
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,960
I may be a flirt,

205
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,200
but I'm still untouched.

206
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,280
Father,

207
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,240
you must stand up for me.

208
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,000
I feared someone
would tamper with things,

209
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,440
