210
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,360
But look at the flower.

211
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:11,920
It still wilted.

212
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,480
This proves

213
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,000
someone is deliberately

214
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,840
trying to frame me for losing my purity

215
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,120
to ruin my reputation!

216
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,480
That's unforgivable, Father.

217
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:20,760
Madam Wang,

218
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,320
