220
00:09:27,154 --> 00:09:27,862
Master...

221
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,560
It was me.

222
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,000
I lost my judgment.

223
00:09:30,428 --> 00:09:30,840
Yes.

224
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,880
I took

225
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,120
a bribe from Mr. Gao.

226
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:33,920
You...

227
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:34,960
That's nonsense!

228
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,440
When did I ever bribe you?

229
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,240
Brother, hear me out.

230
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:38,800
Shut up!

231
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,200
Don't call me brother.

232
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,880
From this day forward,

233
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,000
you are no longer part of the Lu family.

234
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:45,600
Get out!

235
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:46,720
And you too!

236
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,880
Both of you, leave the Lu residence!

237
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:49,520
Out!

238
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,320
Don't you think

239
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,320
the air in the Lu Residence

240
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:26,200
feels clearer
ever since Mr. Gao was thrown out?

241
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:28,680
To me,

242
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,520
the air here

243
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,640
