246
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:41,720
Thank you.

247
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,080
No need.

248
00:10:44,182 --> 00:10:45,400
That's what I'm here for

249
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,960
