250
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,080
You heard that?

251
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,200
Heard what?

252
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:55,800
Then, explain it.

253
00:10:57,514 --> 00:10:58,040
Forget it.

254
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,840
There's nothing to explain.

255
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,400
Either way,

256
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,400
I'm still going to marry Shen Mochen.

257
00:11:06,605 --> 00:11:08,440
What if I say I object?

258
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,651
And what position

259
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,560
are you in to disapprove?

260
00:11:15,497 --> 00:11:16,720
I just don't want to.

261
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,480
You...

262
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,240
Shh.

263
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,280
Do you really mean to be

264
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,200
so cold and heartless?

265
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:50,440
Do you really enjoy

266
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,960
being two-faced

267
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,240
in front of everyone?

268
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,960
That's how

269
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,280
you fooled Shen Mochen, right?

270
00:11:58,920 --> 00:11:59,640
Fine, I admit it.

271
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,760
I did fall for you.

272
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,440
But so what?

273
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,200
I need to save Xiaorou.

274
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,840
I need to run the Foundling Home.

275
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:10,200
I still have to stay alert
around your parents.

276
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:13,960
Love is a luxury to me.

277
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,560
I don't have the time

278
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,360
or the heart for it.

279
00:12:17,377 --> 00:12:18,640
♪My response is ambiguous♪

280
00:12:18,737 --> 00:12:20,040
♪Against my heart♪

281
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,400
I must head for the Wenrou Lounge.

282
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,000
Mr. Siyan,

283
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,000
so long.

284
00:12:25,171 --> 00:12:26,622
♪With yours♪

285
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:28,720
