♪Praying for the ones I love and hate♪

291
00:12:46,171 --> 00:12:49,891
♪Can hold on for a few more years♪

292
00:12:50,017 --> 00:12:55,994
♪But who can truly leave unscathed?♪

293
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:59,080
♪You are the peerless one
with a quiet gaze♪

294
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,720
(Lin Chuning,)

295
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:03,240
(I won't let you marry another man.)

296
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,080
Lin Chuning,

297
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,280
what's the meaning of this money?

298
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,720
You're apologizing?

299
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:15,480
You had the nerve
to kick me out of the family.

300
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,960
Don't come trying
to make peace with cash now!

301
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,560
Do you think

302
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,880
I'd even talk to you

303
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,480
if it weren't to save Xiaorou?

304
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:27,440
You should be thanking me on your knees

305
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,200
for the fact that I didn't end you.

306
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,400
Back to business.

307
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,000
Kicking you out of the Lu family

308
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:37,360
was just a cover

309
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,080
for secretly moving assets.

310
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:40,720
During this time,

311
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:43,080
you'd better take good care of Xiaorou.

312
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,320
Otherwise,

313
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,520
I won't let you off easy.

314
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,320
As long as you cooperate,

315
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,520
this cage you're in

316
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:55,160
will be replaced
with a golden one soon enough.

317
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:12,760
Which looks better?

318
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:13,840
Both.

319
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:17,400
Wrap up everything
my fiancée picked out.

320
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,080
Ms. Lin.

321
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,640
The young master gave orders.

322
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:24,600
If you or Chief Shen come to shop for
wedding gifts or dowries, we won't sell.

323
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,080
It's alright.

324
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:28,760
Let's look elsewhere.

325
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,640
This one's nice.

326
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,400
Take it out so I can have a look.

327
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:45,200
No need.

328
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,480
Wrap that up for me.

329
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:48,360
The young master said

330
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,320
as long as it's you,

331
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,148
we're not selling.

332
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:53,560
It's fine.

333
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:54,720
Let's look elsewhere.

334
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,160
Not for sale?

335
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,120
I'll pay myself.

336
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,280
The young master instructed.

337
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,560
If you're shopping with Chief Shen,

338
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:10,280
we're not selling, period.

339
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:11,880
Chuning.

340
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:12,920
It's okay.

341
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:15,840
The Lu Department Stores
aren't the only ones in town.

342
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:17,800
We'll go somewhere else.

343
00:15:23,457 --> 00:15:25,051
There are plenty of department stores.

344
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,880
But there's only one Lin Chuning.

345
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:29,080
He's not good enough for you.

346
00:15:30,554 --> 00:15:32,200
Everything in Lu Department Stores

347
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,440
belongs to her.

348
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,160
From now on, whatever she wants,

349
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,880
send it straight to her room.

350
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:39,520
Brother,

351
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:42,160
I'm about to marry your sister.

352
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:43,800
She really dotes on you.

353
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,600
So for today,

354
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,440
I'll let it slide.

355
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,240
What happens between me and my sister

356
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:56,840
is none of your business.

357
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:58,920
You haven't married her yet.

358
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:00,880
Stay out of our relationship.

359
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,640
Well, well, Mr. Siyan.

360
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,360
Where have you been lately?

361
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,360
You haven't come looking for me.

362
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,240
I missed you so much.

363
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,560
Can't you see I'm talking?

364
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:28,760
Take it back.

365
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:29,840
I don't need this.

366
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:31,920
Chuning.

367
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:34,360
Mochen,

368
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:35,520
let's go.

369
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,160
Excuse us.

370
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:38,240
Thank you.

371
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,760
Mr. Siyan...

372
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:47,160
Get lost.

373
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,160
Leave!

374
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:14,200
Chuning.

375
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:16,480
What happened that day

376
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:17,600
was not on purpose.

377
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,320
But I never expected

378
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,880
you'd still agree to get engaged to me.

379
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:24,280
Mochen,

380
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:26,680
you and Mr. Gao

381
00:17:27,320 --> 00:17:28,360
were in on it together,

382
00:17:28,360 --> 00:17:29,240
weren't you?

383
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:34,240
Jing is my father's precious daughter.

384
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,120
If you broke off the engagement,

385
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:37,160
if it were me,

386
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:38,960
my father would never agree.

387
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:41,240
But if I lost my purity,

388
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:42,680
and it was with Mr. Gao,

389
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:44,440
then to save face,

390
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:46,640
my father would have to give me up.

391
00:17:47,080 --> 00:17:47,720
So in the end,

392
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,560
you three abandoned me

393
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:52,120
all over again.

394
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,040
Chuning,

395
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,600
I would never abandon you.

396
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:00,960
I'm the only one who won't leave you.

397
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:03,640
The Lu family,

398
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:05,600
and even Lu Siyan,

399
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:07,840
can't be trusted.

400
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:09,680
But I am different.

401
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:12,240
No matter what you have done,

402
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,520
or what you want to do,

403
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,320
I will always

404
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,560
stand by you.

405
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,160
It's getting dark.

406
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,560
Prepare for the engagement banquet.

407
00:18:35,628 --> 00:18:35,960
Alright.

408
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:38,760
I'm really looking forward to that day.

409
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:50,200
You like eavesdropping that much?

410
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:54,680
Seems to me

411
00:18:55,251 --> 00:18:56,840
you don't trust him all that much.

412
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,280
I don't trust him.

413
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,040
I don't trust you either.

414
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:04,548
I don't think you really doubt me.

415
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,360
At first,

416
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:08,640
you planned to use the banquet
as cover to rescue Xiaorou.

417
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,200
But after the drama
with Shen Mochen and your uncle,

418
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,360
the banquet got canceled.

419
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:15,000
So you just went along with the change

420
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:17,280
and asked Shen Mochen
for an engagement party.

421
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,280
Am I right?

422
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:21,520
Correct.

423
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,440
But that doesn't mean

424
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,040
I will marry you.

425
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:27,280
Before this,

426
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,800
you wanted to use my lowly status

427
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:31,320
to rebel against your parents.

428
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:33,160
You always knew

429
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,760
there was never any future

430
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:36,320
for the two of us.

431
00:19:37,691 --> 00:19:38,960
Whether there's a future or not

432
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,040
has nothing to do with status.

433
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:43,160
It all comes down to feelings.

434
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:45,000
I didn't love you before.

435
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,320
But now I do.

436
00:19:48,737 --> 00:19:49,800
So it doesn't matter

437
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:50,920
who you are.

438
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,737
Even if Mr. Gao didn't succeed,

439
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,480
I still...

440
00:19:55,525 --> 00:19:57,840
You are in no mood
to talk about love right now.

441
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,600
I just want to secure my place first.

442
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:01,640
Once you're done with everything,

443
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:02,760
I'll be waiting.

444
00:20:04,588 --> 00:20:05,874
For the life ahead of you,

445
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:07,640
I'll be there for you.

446
00:20:08,765 --> 00:20:10,765
♪Even for a moment?♪

447
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,960
I want you to know this.

448
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,480
Just like a torchlight,

449
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:15,880
I hope

450
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:18,360
to be the light in your heart.

451
00:20:18,914 --> 00:20:21,028
♪You're the moon above the trees♪

452
00:20:21,051 --> 00:20:22,925
♪The finest of all in charm and ease♪

453
00:20:23,057 --> 00:20:27,154
♪Born with eyes
that hold the world's desire♪

454
00:20:27,337 --> 00:20:29,365
♪By my pillow lies your name♪

455
00:20:29,462 --> 00:20:31,525
♪In dreams,
my heart still burns the same♪

456
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:35,114
♪You took my hand
to ride beneath the stars♪

457
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:41,520
(As long as Lin Chuning lives,)

458
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:43,800
(Siyan will remain in danger.)

459
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:46,120
(Lin Chuning,)

460
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,760
(you should have
stayed away from your brother.)

461
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,680
(You never should have come.)

462
00:20:51,380 --> 00:20:51,900
(I'm here)

463
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:53,280
(Chuning,)

464
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,440
(Fear not)
(don't be scared.)

465
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:56,200
(I'll always be with you.)

466
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,440
(Lu Siyan,)

467
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:03,080
(thank you.)

468
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:10,980
(Fear not)

469
00:21:10,980 --> 00:21:12,971
(Lu Residence)

470
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:15,720
Jing threw a fit when she heard
you're getting engaged

471
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:16,840
to Chuning.

472
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:19,880
They are both my daughters.

473
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,360
As their mother,

474
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:22,920
this puts me in a tough spot.

475
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,760
All of this is my fault.

476
00:21:27,120 --> 00:21:28,640
I caused both of you trouble.

477
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,440
Nothing wrong with loving someone.

478
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:35,200
Chuning grew up away from home.

479
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,360
She's suffered so much.

480
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:40,280
From now on,

481
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:41,600
I'm counting on you

482
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,560
to take good care of her for us.

483
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:58,600
Don't worry.

484
00:21:59,600 --> 00:22:01,360
I feel exactly the same way as you do.

485
00:22:02,080 --> 00:22:02,840
Chuning will be

486
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:03,760
treated well.

487
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:19,840
Alright.

488
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:21,360
She is waiting at the workshop.

489
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:22,280
Go now.

490
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:26,480
Mother,

491
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:28,800
I'll be going now.

492
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,040
Tell Ms. Lin to go to the workshop.

493
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:38,000
Say the young master needs to see her.

494
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:39,360
Yes.

495
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:08,660
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

496
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:11,520
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

497
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:14,910
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

498
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:18,130
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

499
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:21,880
♪Pushing away the gravel
hidden beneath the seaweed♪

500
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:24,850
♪Wandering near your heart♪

501
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:28,480
♪I imagined
our encounter countless times♪

502
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:31,480
♪So close, yet out of reach♪

503
00:23:32,390 --> 00:23:37,540
♪Keeping
all this lonely courage to myself♪

504
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:44,870
♪I was never part of your world♪

505
00:23:44,960 --> 00:23:48,490
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

506
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:51,540
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

507
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:55,130
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

508
00:23:55,330 --> 00:23:58,250
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

509
00:23:58,310 --> 00:24:01,970
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

510
00:24:02,070 --> 00:24:05,170
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

511
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:10,900
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

512
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:28,620
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

513
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:31,540
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

514
00:24:31,630 --> 00:24:34,950
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

515
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:38,610
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

516
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:42,080
♪Returning to the land
Left bare by the receding sea♪

517
00:24:42,260 --> 00:24:44,970
♪Withering like a fallen leaf♪

518
00:24:45,030 --> 00:24:48,480
♪The message in a bottle
buried on the shore♪

519
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:51,480
♪No one asked♪

520
00:24:52,430 --> 00:24:58,040
♪All this lonely courage for myself♪

521
00:24:58,710 --> 00:25:04,760
♪I'm no longer part of your world♪

522
00:25:04,930 --> 00:25:08,530
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

523
00:25:08,610 --> 00:25:11,620
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

524
00:25:11,670 --> 00:25:15,090
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

525
00:25:15,330 --> 00:25:18,200
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

526
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:21,930
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

527
00:25:22,060 --> 00:25:25,140
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

528
00:25:25,290 --> 00:25:31,250
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

529
00:25:31,610 --> 00:25:35,350
♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

530
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:38,220
♪And swim with me to you♪

531
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:41,810
♪I'd become♪

532
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:44,870
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

533
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:48,540
♪If love is like a night storm♪

534
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:51,810
♪Unable to stop for a moment♪

535
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:57,700
♪Let the wind scatter my traces♪
